{"type":"message","id":"af545804","parentId":"6f7f9dcb","timestamp":"2026-05-13T09:27:54.833Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我看到了配置。你有多个飞书账号（Agent）：\n- kiit（KIIT主账号）\n- tts（选品大师）\n- agent-orchestrator（Agent编掔工程师）\n\n这些是不同的飞书机器人账号。用户问的是这些Agent之间如何互通。\n\n从配置来看，每个Agent都是一个独立的飞书账号。它们之间的互通可以是：\n\n1. **飞书消息互通** - 通过飞书API，让一个机器人给另一个机器人发消息\n2. **OpenClaw底层会话** - 通过sessions_send等API\n\n实际上，从架构上看，这些Agent本质上是独立的飞书bot账号。它们可以通过飞书消息互发，也可以通过OpenClaw的底层会话机制。\n\n让我检查一下是否有更多关于现有架构的信息。\n","thinkingSignature":"db4de68eec89d0e39bceceb7ad21868a967cbf6b61aeb2c11a35934fa47f0a95"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mcejqyfdjiax_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la ~/.openclaw/agents/"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mcejqyfdjiax_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json 2>/dev/null | python3 -m json.tool 2>/dev/null | grep -A 30 '\"agents\"'"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1617,"output":234,"cacheRead":20224,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22075,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778664449875,"responseId":"06537702e49944befb03b5c2f2ba3ae1"}}
