{"type":"message","id":"741098e5","parentId":"b667dff2","timestamp":"2026-05-13T09:28:38.312Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是\"目前创建的一些Agent，要让它们如何实现互通呢？是用飞书的这个消息互通来去协作，还是用什么，用openlo底层的那个互通方式\"\n\n从配置来看：\n1. 每个 Agent 都有一个独立的飞书账号（appId/appSecret）\n2. 每个 Agent 绑定到不同的飞书账号，实现与人类的对话\n3. 飞书是作为\"入口\"——人类通过飞书与各个 Agent 交互\n\n但 Agent 之间如何通信？\n- 从 bindings 配置看，每个 agent 绑定到一个飞书账号\n- 但 Agent 之间的通信... 没有看到专门的配置\n\n在 OpenClaw 中，Agent 之间的通信方式有：\n1. **sessions_send** - 直接在 session 之间发送消息（OpenClaw 底层）\n2. **共享黑板/文件** - 通过共享存储进行数据交换\n3. **飞书消息** - 通过飞书频道发消息给其他 Agent 的飞书账号\n\n让我看看现有的 agent workspace 里有没有关于通信的配置。\n","thinkingSignature":"ec4044eded003402a0c9236e341e8923b06879a62cbab2b00cf8ee6882ef5db0"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xm441eo88b5r_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/agents/agent-orchestrator/"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xm441eo88b5r_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/agents/tts/"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":721,"output":270,"cacheRead":23040,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24031,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778664489242,"responseId":"06537729bebb1ea86543d6a999745b11"}}
