{"type":"message","id":"0f9522aa","parentId":"cef193f9","timestamp":"2026-05-13T09:29:58.881Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. Let me summarize the current architecture:\n\n**Current Setup:**\n- Multiple agents (main, tts, agent-orchestrator, content, traffic, ops, director, finance, review, koc)\n- Each has its own workspace and its own Feishu account (appId/appSecret)\n- Each agent is bound to its own Feishu account via bindings\n- Each agent is effectively isolated - it only receives messages sent to its own Feishu bot\n\n**The question is: how do these agents communicate with each other?**\n\nCurrently they don't automatically communicate. Each agent is bound to its own Feishu account, meaning:\n- main receives messages sent to KITT-AGI bot\n- tts receives messages sent to 选品大师 bot\n- etc.\n\nFor agent-to-agent communication, there are two realistic options:\n\n1. **Feishu inter-bot communication**: One agent sends a message via Feishu to another bot. But this is complex because each bot has its own appId and would need to use the Feishu API to send messages to other bots by their open_id.\n\n2. **OpenClaw native sessions_send**: Use the sessions_send tool to send messages directly between agent sessions without going through Feishu.\n\nThe user is asking which method is being used currently. The answer is: **currently these agents are NOT automatically互通**. They're isolated by design. Each agent only responds to messages directed to its own Feishu bot.\n\nIf the user wants to enable互通, they would need to either:\n1. Use sessions_send for direct OpenClaw communication\n2. Or set up some kind of hub/spoke model where one agent acts as coordinator\n\nLet me give a clear, direct answer.\n","thinkingSignature":"54931996c706b2514a761098447573fbac02eb1533c05e0b6239a7e52e2ae3e8"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n看了你的配置，现在回答你的问题：\n\n## 当前互通协议：**飞书 + 完全隔离**\n\n你的每个 Agent 目前都是**独立绑定的飞书 Bot**：\n\n| Agent | 飞书 Bot | 绑定方式 |\n|-------|---------|---------|\n| main | KITT-AGI (kiit) | 接收发送到该 Bot 的消息 |\n| tts | 选品大师 (tts) | 接收发送到该 Bot 的消息 |\n| agent-orchestrator | 编掔工程师 | 接收发送到该 Bot 的消息 |\n| content | 内容专家 | 接收发送到该 Bot 的消息 |\n| ... | ... | ... |\n\n**每个 Agent 只响应发到自己的飞书消息**，它们之间目前**没有自动互通机制**。\n\n---\n\n## 如何实现互通？\n\n有两种方式：\n\n### 方式一：OpenClaw 底层会话（推荐）\n用 `sessions_send` 在不同 Agent 的 session 之间直接发消息：\n\n```javascript\n// Agent A 调用 sessions_send 给 Agent B\nsessions_send({\n  sessionKey: \"tts\",  // 目标 agent session\n  message: \"帮我选品: 女装春款\"\n})\n```\n\n**优点**：低延迟、可编程、不依赖飞书\n**缺点**：需要人类观察调试\n\n### 方式二：飞书 Bot 间消息\n让一个 Agent 通过飞书 API 给另一个 Bot 发消息，需要：\n- 知道对方的 open_id\n- 调用飞书 API 发送\n\n**缺点**：复杂、延迟高、不适合高频协作\n\n---\n\n## 建议\n\n如果想让 Agent 之间自动协作，**推荐用 OpenClaw 的 sessions_send 机制**，配合共享黑板/状态文件来协调。\n\n你想让哪些 Agent 之间互通？我可以帮你设计具体的通信架构。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1990,"output":721,"cacheRead":23808,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26519,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778664530080,"responseId":"06537752ab4edae226ec3b536a09c471"}}
